Package Manager

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Class
    The Class object represents a class.
    Manager
    The Manager object is based on section 2.2 of the requirements.
    Page
    Derived from section 2.2.
    Section
    Represents a section of a class.
    Tutorial
    Derived from section 2.2 A tutorial is a collection of information pages and quizzes.
    Unit
    Derived from section 2.2 A Unit is a collection of tutorials, making one cohesive section about a range of subjects.
    User
    The user class is based on the requirement that classes need students.
    UserDB
    A collection of users to be used when creating new classes or sections.
